    "name": "Mesh Independence Study — FDA Generic Centrifugal Pump",
    "description": "Systematic grid refinement study conducted across three mesh densities (coarse: 2.1M cells, medium: 6.4M cells, fine: 18.7M cells) to establish discretization error bounds for the CFD hemolysis prediction model. Richardson extrapolation applied to pressure head and wall shear stress distributions at five operating points spanning the clinical flow range (3–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Grid convergence index (GCI) computed per Celik et al. (2008) methodology.",
    "activityType": "GridConvergenceStudy",
    "performedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/org/morrison-lab",
